race.comment: STYLE CAT (8) has been out of the placings in two runs since a break, the latest when seventh, beaten 1.5 lengths, over 1006m at Del Mar (Turf) after he travelled towards the rear of the field. First try at the trip but he strips fitter and looks set to find best form. BROSKI (6) was comfortably accounted for when tenth last time out over 1609m at Del Mar, beaten 7 lengths after being in contention on the corner. That followed a win at Del Mar at the previous outing. Yet to miss the frame in three starts over this course and distance. Perfectly placed and is sure to take a ton of beating. MYTHICAL REEL (1) impressed first-up then took on a much better race last time when fifth over 1811m in the G2 Del Mar Derby (Turf). One of the chances based on his best recent efforts. MAAZ (4) was below his best last time when 11th over 2213m at Del Mar (Turf), beaten 5.5 lengths. Suitably placed so anticipating a better run this time.
